description:
Now the souls are one…

Collin has not given up hope, he climbs down the chasm to find the amulet and to find Sallian. He finds himself in another world where Sallian has been trapped since she fell. Believing that she will not survive, their true feelings fro each other are exposed and they make passionate love. Will Collin save Feelia from her alternate personalities and how will she reward him?
title: Princess Memory II
